{"tid":288227,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士擬售月票吸客 或設手機app留座","createTime":"2017-06-18T04:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T05:14:33.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"637d800238d221948efc16692a3315e56d203b76","tid":288227,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T04:47:18.000Z","msg":"巴士擬售月票吸客 或設手機app留座<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n2017-06-18 11:53:11 HKT<br />\n<br />\n立法會鐵路事宜小組委員會主席田北辰在電台節目透露，有專營巴士公司有意推出月票，惟政府對巴士公司的規限較港鐵高，有巴士公司認為不公平。田北辰認為，若巴士公司推出月票「全港通」，售價低於700元，相信會有吸引力。<br />\n<br />\n對於政府早前建議推行「優質巴士」，行駛新界至市區的長途路線，車上只設座位，田北辰認為優質巴士有吸引力，更透露有巴士公司或推出手機留座服務，「每朝早食完早餐未落街，就可以喺手機app訂下一架車嘅座位」，相信不少市民願意乘搭。<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"861342c7066bf0644c8c8187394cda1c77d40fbd","tid":288227,"uid":21120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T04:49:14.000Z","msg":"7舊水<br />\n除左搭機場A車返工<br />\n點搭先回本"},{"pid":"c88eada47832f8d283a8189d2efc0401cf598fbe","tid":288227,"uid":2247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T04:49:58.000Z","msg":"400 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b443bedc174a14d522b8bf4c13b5dc4e5a85e18","tid":288227,"uid":60052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T04:51:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>7舊水<br />\n除左搭機場A車返工<br />\n點搭先回本</blockquote><br />\n佢當人返足30日工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d418cd943019ed814baea292b76c0b6252d79ab","tid":288227,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T04:52:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>7舊水<br />\n除左搭機場A車返工<br />\n點搭先回本</blockquote><br />\n新界至港島過海巴士"},{"pid":"c20c4ec2f13f4e075e0587cdb32e53f107506079","tid":288227,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T04:53:36.000Z","msg":"如果有嘅 我有賺 因為一個月車費最少880蚊"},{"pid":"5afb43f0f2c092beee8c5c71e6da2fd1858fe13b","tid":288227,"